name: Taco Clicker! (Impac)
description:
Click the taco to earn tacos! 

Open the shop for different kinds of upgrades and boosts!

Hotkeys:

T: alternate way of clicking the taco

S: Toggles the shop

Inspired by all other clicker games

Extra info:

Hi! it's me, the creator of taco clicker.

i would give a lot of credit to Fuelvin for the tutorial on how to make the game.
